Input - A .pslx file from blat.

Options:
  -h, --help    show a help message and exit
  -i INNAME     Input filename
  -o OUTNAME    Output filename
  -l LENGTH     Minimum length of the *sum* of the blocks greater than
                MIN_BLOCK. Default=960
  -s MIN_BLOCK  Minimum size for an individual block to be considered.
                Default=80
